  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/6684335/" class="title-link">辛德勇《建元与改元》中的各种吐槽</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-6684335"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/51399394/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u51399394-5.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/51399394/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">或曰</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2014-05-28"
      class="main-meta">2014-05-28 15:58:59</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_6684335_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  买了好几本辛德勇的书，但之前只读过《读书与藏书之间》，并没有很特别的印象。近日读他的《建元与改元》，即刻膜拜！作者读书之博、考辨之精，让人惊异。尤其激动的是那种千回百转的辨析简直令人不忍释卷，而书中对古今中外学者的各种吐槽，太欢乐了，我怀疑作者是不是练了千...

