  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="6384124">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/6384124/" class="title-link">转 陈晓珊：《建元与改元》:历史学的本格推理</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-6384124"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/14494088/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u14494088-1.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/14494088/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">变幻自在</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2013-11-07"
      class="main-meta">2013-11-07 20:44:30</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_6384124_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  在这瞬息万变的人世间，真实的生活常比虚构的故事更富想象力。经过千百年沉淀的历史更是如此，时空的变迁为往事增加了神秘感，消磨在岁月中的证据让实情更加扑朔迷离。或许在不期而至的某一天，沉睡千载的物证破土而出，指向青史中毫无关联的过客，让早已被人遗忘的旧事再起波...

